11:11.577 --> 11:13.944
Don't drag hibachi into this, man.

11:14.046 --> 11:15.612
That's 'bachi, dude! 'Bachi!

11:15.664 --> 11:16.713
And you're only saying that

11:16.815 --> 11:17.915
because you know I'm right about Derek.

11:17.940 --> 11:18.944
