I want to watch him eat cereal

11:24.123 --> 11:26.523
and talk about changing the air filter.

11:26.592 --> 11:28.659
Okay? It's confusing.

11:28.761 --> 11:32.102
- Thank you.
- But you owe Douglas an explanation,

11:32.180 --> 11:34.965
and you're just putting it on me
because you know I'm right.

11:34.990 --> 11:36.001
No, you're just making this about me

11:36.035 --> 11:37.077
because you know I'm right.

11:37.102 --> 11:38.569
I'm out.

11:38.637 --> 11:40.637
Also, Derek's been standing behind you

11:40.739 --> 11:42.760
this whole time,
