I did hear everything,

11:49.548 --> 11:50.948
but I'm willing to have my mind wiped

11:51.050 --> 11:52.482
if you'll loan me the money.

11:57.256 --> 11:58.522
There's Dad's car!

11:58.591 --> 12:00.857
It's not a car.
It's a gentleman's coupe.

12:00.926 --> 12:02.125
Show some respect.

12:02.194 --> 12:05.028
Wow. I gotta say, I am impressed, Rory.

12:05.130 --> 12:06.630
You really do know Douglas.

12:06.699 --> 12:08.398
See, Miggy? All's well that ends well.

12:08.500 --> 12:10.167
Or should I say, ends Will?

12:10.269 --> 12:11.501
I don't like that, man.

12:11.604 --> 12:13.804
It's true, guys.
I really do know Douglas.

12:13.906 --> 12:16.073
I've really gotten
to know him this past year.

12:16.175 --> 12:18.875
We've become very close.

12:18.978 --> 12:20.077
Which is why it's a shame

12:20.179 --> 12:21.178
that he has broken my mom's heart

12:21.280 --> 12:22.679
and now I must murder him.

12:24.493 --> 12:25.559
- Go. Go, go, go, go, go!
- What?!

12:25.584 --> 12:27.184
- Rory? Rory?
- Go, go! Let's go!

12:27.286 --> 12:29.319
- Murder is fun!
- Move! Move!

12:29.421 --> 12:31.496
Museums are for learning!

12:32.493 --> 12:36.330
Uh, okay. So, did you h-hear
the part where...

12:36.409 --> 12:38.932
I heard all the parts.
Especially the one where you said

12:39.002 --> 12:40.534
you wanted to be
in a relationship with me?

12:40.622 --> 12:41.821
I said maybe.

12:41.889 --> 12:43.389
And I was in a fight
with my best friend.

12:43.458 --> 12:45.625
That's legally the same as being drunk.

12:45.693 --> 12:47.793
You don't have to backpedal. This is...

12:47.895 --> 12:50.096
It's obviously a-a sexy situation...

12:50.198 --> 12:52.231
No, no, no. This is not sexy.

12:52.333 --> 12:54.634
And this is definitely not a situation.

12:54.736 --> 12:58.871
Oh, well, that's a bummer.
Because... the truth is,

12:58.940 --> 13:00.921
I want that, too.

13:00.991 --> 13:02.208
I want to be with you.

13:02.310 --> 13:03.976
What?

13:04.078 --> 13:05.945
- You do?
- I do.

13:06.047 --> 13:08.047
Very much.

13:08.149 --> 13:10.216
Well...

13:10.285 --> 13:12.785
We're just getting into a really
good co-parenting rhythm,

13:12.887 --> 13:14.053
and I... I don't...

13:14.122 --> 13:15.915
I don't want to do anything
that'll risk that.

13:15.993 --> 13:17.757
I know. I totally agree.

13:17.825 --> 13:19.959
But also, what if we just did?

13:20.028 --> 13:22.461
Listen, Graham goes to camp
every summer.

13:22.563 --> 13:24.563
What if you came with me
to Barstow while he's away?

13:24.632 --> 13:26.098
We could figure out what this is.

13:26.200 --> 13:28.434
You could finally get to know Phoebe.

13:28.536 --> 13:29.535
That's my turtle.

13:29.637 --> 13:31.937
Yeah, I know. She sent me a valentine.

13:32.006 --> 13:33.706
That was from me.

13:33.808 --> 13:35.541
Yeah, I figured.

13:35.610 --> 13:37.943
If we don't try, we'll always wonder.

13:39.380 --> 13:41.947
Mom, Derek, look what I made!

13:42.050 --> 13:43.649
I didn't even use instructions.

13:43.751 --> 13:45.017
But it looks great, right?

13:45.086 --> 13:47.019
That makes me want to be a real LEGO man

13:47.121 --> 13:48.387
so I can fly it.

13:48.456 --> 13:50.256
You see... you see these orange ones?

13:50.325 --> 13:53.592
Basically, this thing here,
this is actually laser-proof.

13:53.695 --> 13:54.860
- Laser-proof?
- Yeah.

13:54.962 --> 13:57.930
- And, um, right in here...
- Yeah?

13:57.999 --> 14:00.166
This is where they eat snacks.

14:00.234 --> 14:02.268
- Oh, that's a snack hole?
- Yeah.

14:02.337 --> 14:05.271
I keep replaying it and replaying it,

14:05.340 --> 14:07.006
and I don't understand it, Dutch.

14:07.075 --> 14:09.809
She was supposed to be my Nancy.

14:09.877 --> 14:11.744
Hello, Douglas.

14:11.813 --> 14:13.546
Rory, what are you doing here?

14:13.648 --> 14:14.680
I have come to murder you.

14:14.782 --> 14:16.549
And that would go down how?

14:16.651 --> 14:20.119
I mean, I figured I could
find something to throw at you.

14:20.221 --> 14:21.328
Maybe a sword.

14:21.406 --> 14:23.171
Feel like a lot of museums have swords.

14:24.325 --> 14:25.691
I don't know. I'm just mad at you.

14:25.793 --> 14:27.326
Well, I'm mad at me, too.

14:27.395 --> 14:29.395
Your mom was the greatest thing
that ever happened to me,

14:29.464 --> 14:30.863
and... and I blew it.

14:30.932 --> 14:32.431
Then she broke up with me.

14:32.533 --> 14:36.001
Wait. She broke up with you?

14:36.070 --> 14:37.703
- Why?
- I-I don't know.

14:37.805 --> 14:38.771
She never told me.

14:38.840 --> 14:40.506
But you know your mom...
she's a smart woman,

14:40.608 --> 14:43.542
so she must have had a good reason.

14:45.012 --> 14:47.113
Well, this sucks.

14:47.181 --> 14:48.914
You know, I didn't like you
for a long time.

14:49.016 --> 14:51.417
- Same.
- Mm.

14:51.486 --> 14:53.586
But now I do.

14:53.688 --> 14:54.820
Same.

14:54.889 --> 14:57.189
So, we came all this way,

14:57.291 --> 14:59.525
and now, just like that,
you're out of my life?

14:59.627 --> 15:01.260
Hey, Rory,

15:01.329 --> 15:03.496
I will never be out of your life.

15:03.564 --> 15:05.364
Okay? Look at me. Look at me!

15:05.466 --> 15:07.166
- I'm looking straight at you.
- I know.

15:07.235 --> 15:09.668
It just sounded like
the right thing to say.

15:09.737 --> 15:12.438
Listen, whatever happens
between me and your mom

15:12.507 --> 15:14.807
won't change how I feel about you.

15:14.909 --> 15:17.710
You will always be a part of my life.

15:17.812 --> 15:20.559
And I'm always here for you. Okay?

15:26.320 --> 15:27.420
- Mm. Mnh. Nope.
- Yeah.

15:27.488 --> 15:28.654
All right, let's never
talk about that again.

15:28.756 --> 15:31.424
- Talk about what?
- Nice.

15:31.526 --> 15:32.792
Look, you're not a quitter.

15:32.894 --> 15:35.694
If you want to get Poppy back,
you gotta at least try.

15:38.599 --> 15:41.901
Scale of one to ten,
how racist was that fella?

15:42.003 --> 15:43.569
I'm done with you now.

15:46.908 --> 15:48.741
Excuse me, sir, our friend went in there

15:48.843 --> 15:49.942
to "kill" our other friend,

15:50.011 --> 15:51.177
and we have to get in to stop it.

15:51.245 --> 15:52.411
Do you have a reservation?

15:52.480 --> 15:54.313
You need a reservation
for the Ronnie Room?

15:54.415 --> 15:57.349
This is more government control
than the Gipper would've wanted.

15:57.452 --> 15:59.118
And you know that.

15:59.187 --> 16:00.786
Come on. Let's go touch some stuff.

16:00.855 --> 16:02.788
Okay, you were right.

16:02.890 --> 16:05.257
Clearly Douglas doesn't want us
anywhere near him.

16:05.326 --> 16:06.492
This is such a mess.

16:06.561 --> 16:07.993
This is why friends
shouldn't date within the group.

16:08.062 --> 16:10.663
It's too risky.
That's why I would never do it.

16:10.765 --> 16:12.064
Uh...

16:12.166 --> 16:13.232
I'm gonna say disagree.

16:13.301 --> 16:15.401
I got mad respect for Poppy and Douglas.

16:15.470 --> 16:16.969
They had the guts to take a shot.

16:17.038 --> 16:18.471
The only thing worse than a breakup

16:18.573 --> 16:20.339
is letting those feelings eat you up.

16:20.441 --> 16:22.408
I could never do that.

16:22.510 --> 16:23.909
Could you?

16:32.220 --> 16:34.220
Okay! Gonna go check out some T-Rexes.

16:34.322 --> 16:37.056
Um, different kind of museum, buddy.

16:37.124 --> 16:38.424
Nah, I'll find 'em.

16:44.232 --> 16:45.598
Ding dong.

16:45.666 --> 16:47.366
I'm sorry.

16:47.468 --> 16:48.767
Look...

16:50.171 --> 16:51.528
...you were right, all right?

16:51.606 --> 16:54.240
I may have some
unresolved feelings for Derek.

16:54.308 --> 16:55.508
And he told me he does, too.

16:55.610 --> 16:58.177
- What? He said that?
- Later. Save that for later.

16:58.254 --> 16:59.545
All right.

16:59.647 --> 17:00.813
I didn't want to hear the truth,

17:00.882 --> 17:03.949
but... you're a good friend
for telling me anyway.

17:04.050 --> 17:05.483
You are, too.

17:05.586 --> 17:07.219
I know. I need to talk to Douglas.

17:07.320 --> 17:08.521
I just... I don't know where to start.

17:08.623 --> 17:10.923
You know him better than anyone.

17:10.992 --> 17:13.025
And just... talk.

17:13.127 --> 17:14.527
Even if it's tough.

17:14.628 --> 17:16.228
Like a piece of hibachi steak.

17:16.329 --> 17:18.998
Okay, you go for the experience.

17:21.002 --> 17:24.869
And you were right about my yoga pants.

17:24.939 --> 17:26.238
