17:26.307 --> 17:29.241
I know, baby. I know.

17:34.958 --> 17:36.415
That coffee for me?

17:36.517 --> 17:38.751
Yes. They... they wrote "Poopy" on it.

17:38.853 --> 17:40.686
- Oh.
- Yeah, I'm sorry.

17:40.755 --> 17:43.188
I'm just honestly seeing that
for the first time.

17:43.257 --> 17:45.224
I actually got you a coffee, too.

17:45.293 --> 17:47.126
Guess we were both hoping
we'd run into each other.

17:47.228 --> 17:49.228
- I guess so.
- Should we exchange coffees...

17:49.297 --> 17:52.763
Listen, Pop, I-I could ease into this
with some light banter,

17:52.849 --> 17:55.334
but I-I know what I want... you.

17:55.403 --> 17:57.591
And I'll do whatever it takes
to get you back.

17:57.637 --> 17:59.520
Douglas, I don't think
you can promise that.

17:59.567 --> 18:00.817
Yes, I can.

18:00.895 --> 18:02.875
If you want me to quit my job,
I'll quit my job.

18:02.944 --> 18:05.044
If you want to move
to another city, I will.

18:05.146 --> 18:07.012
Just not Santa Fe. Creeps me out.

18:07.114 --> 18:09.114
O-Okay, Santa Fe.

18:09.216 --> 18:11.083
I'll move to Santa Fe for you.

18:11.152 --> 18:13.152
Douglas, I want to have a baby.

18:14.589 --> 18:15.988
A baby?

18:16.090 --> 18:18.457
Wow. That is, uh...

18:18.559 --> 18:22.494
Like one that takes 18 years to raise?

18:22.597 --> 18:24.263
A-Are you... Oh, okay.

18:24.332 --> 18:26.031
You know... You know what?
Let's... Let's do it.

18:26.133 --> 18:27.166
Let's do the baby.

18:27.268 --> 18:29.602
Come on. You... You don't
want that, do you?

18:29.704 --> 18:30.970
I want us.

18:31.072 --> 18:33.639
I do, too, but I can't let you
have a baby that you don't want.

18:33.741 --> 18:35.508
That won't make either one of us happy.

18:37.712 --> 18:40.139
Okay, so I guess this is just a...

18:40.202 --> 18:43.983
Horrible, sucky,
unfixable situation. Yeah.

18:44.085 --> 18:47.219
Oh, man. Yeah, that's...
that's the worst kind.

18:47.321 --> 18:49.688
Um...

18:49.790 --> 18:51.156
I'm sorry.

18:51.258 --> 18:52.758
Don't be sorry.

18:54.395 --> 18:55.928
I love you.

18:58.032 --> 18:59.531
I love you, too.

19:02.536 --> 19:04.203
Thanks.

19:19.829 --> 19:21.747
Oh, my God. You were, like, right there.

19:21.797 --> 19:24.059
Yeah, you're an incredibly loud
parallel parker.

19:24.114 --> 19:27.182
