to Barstow for the summer.

20:17.998 --> 20:19.231
Oh.

20:19.333 --> 20:20.504
I said that I would think about it.

20:20.567 --> 20:24.036
- Oh?
- And as crazy as it sounds, I...

20:25.439 --> 20:27.606
I might do it.

20:27.708 --> 20:30.409
Ohhhh!

20:30.511 --> 20:33.879
That... is crazy!

20:33.981 --> 20:35.013
And you know what?

20:35.115 --> 20:36.882
I'm gonna go.

20:36.984 --> 20:38.677
Where are you going? You just got here.

20:38.755 --> 20:41.114
To the... beach.

20:41.188 --> 20:42.421
